- `h_cfg_CNF_gen_is_lang : coerceLang α (↑cfg_CNF).Z (↑cfg_CNF).generatedLanguage = coerceLang α (↑cfg_CNF).Z (↑cfg_CNF).generatedLanguage`
- `z : ↑{z | z ∈ ↑language ∧ z.len ≥ 2 ^ (↑cfg_CNF).V.card}`
